# ============================================================
# NEVER commit the Simpsonville corpus (PII)
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# The real Flock/Simpsonville FOIA corpus contains personal data
# (names, DOBs, A-numbers, plate context). It lives OUTSIDE this
# repo (the operator's Downloads) and is referenced for golden
# tests only via an env var (see Task 11.2). Never copy real data
# into the tree. These rules are defensive belt-and-suspenders:
corpus/private/
*-Audit-logs/
*-Audit.csv
*-Network-Audit.csv
**/*[Ss]impsonville*[Aa]udit*
pii_*_exhibit.csv
pretext_exhibit.csv
immigration_exhibit.csv
